(last updated 2012-09-23)

Resource Identifier (RI) Scheme name: platform 
Status: provisional

Scheme syntax:
   platform:/(resource|plugin|fragment|meta|config|base)/...

Scheme semantics:
   Access to Eclipse platform resources.

Encoding considerations:
   Unknown, use with care.

Applications/protocols that use this scheme name:
   Registered with java.net.URL when launching with the org.eclipse.core.filesystem bundle, 
   and heavily leveraged by org.eclipse.emf.common.util.URI.

Interoperability considerations:
   Unknown, use with care.
   May be unsuitable for open use on the public internet.
Security considerations:
   Unknown, use with care.
Contact:
   Registering party: Dave Thaler <dthaler&microsoft.com>
   Scheme creator: Eclipse platform scheme documentation
Author/Change controller:
   Either the registering party or someone who is verified to represent
   the scheme creator.  See previous answer.
References:
   http://help.eclipse.org/indigo/index.jsp?topic=%2Forg.eclipse.platform.doc.isv%2Freference%2Fmisc%2Fplatform-scheme-uri.html


